    <h3>Craft & Ingredients</h3>
    <p>We source single-origin cocoa beans and combine traditional techniques with modern flavors. Our ingredients are carefully selected: real cocoa butter, fresh cream, and responsibly sourced nuts and fruits.</p>
    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
    <p>We partner with small farmers to ensure fair pricing and sustainable farming practices. Our packaging is recyclable and minimal.</p>
    <h3>Quality</h3>
    <p>Each small-batch is manually inspected by our chocolatiers, ensuring consistent texture and flavor.</p>
